Feature: Data Sources

  @addgdrivedetails @ediscobat  @ediscobatnew @twog @ftkcbat
  Scenario Outline: ED-286:Data sources - Add Gdrive details

    When Login to Ediscovery with "<credentials>"
    And Click on widget "Data Sources"
    And Click on connectors "Google Drive"
    And Verify for connectors add "Add Google Drive" is displayed
    And Click on Add "Add Google Drive" button
    And Enter connector details for grive service account "<gdrivedetails>"
    And Navigate to Home Page
    And Click on widget "Data Sources"
    And Verify for connectors add "Add Custodian" is displayed
    And Click on Add "Add Custodian" button
    And Create custodian "<custodian>"
    And Verify Custodian "<custodian>" is displayed
    And Click on connectors "Google Drive"
    And Verify for connectors add "Add Google Drive" is displayed
    And Click on Map Custodain btn for "<gdrivedetails>"
    And Select Custodain "<custodian>" to map
    And Click on Map Custodain btn for "<gdrivedetails>"
    And Verify "<count>" for mapped custodian

    Examples:

      | credentials | gdrivedetails      | custodian         | count |
      | admin       | googledrivedetails | gdriveCustodian01 | 1     |
